== 發行 ==
2015年1月，任天堂在網絡直播節目[[任天堂直面會|任天堂直面會]]上宣佈推出一系列3DS遊戲，其中包括火焰之紋章系列新作<ref name="Famitsu@150115">{{Cite web |url = https://www.famitsu.com/news/201501/15069514.html |script-title = ja:【Nintendo Directまとめ（3DS）】『FE』完全新作、『ゼノブレイド』、『ムジュラの仮面』などニンテンドー3DSの胸躍る新情報総まとめ |date = 2015-01-15 |publisher = ファミ通.com |language = ja |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220126013216/https://www.famitsu.com/news/201501/15069514.html |archivedate = 2022-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.polygon.com/2015/1/14/7545155/new-fire-emblem-coming-to-nintendo-3ds |title = New Fire Emblem coming to Nintendo 3DS |last = Farokhmanesh |first = Megan |date = 2015-01-14 |publisher = Polygon |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210925184128/https://www.polygon.com/2015/1/14/7545155/new-fire-emblem-coming-to-nintendo-3ds |archivedate = 2021-09-25}}</ref>。當時任天堂社長[[岩田聰|岩田聰]]揭露新作名稱為「火焰之紋章if」<ref name="Famitsu@150115"/>。在同年6月舉行的[[2015年電子娛樂展|電子娛樂展]]上，任天堂披露英文版遊戲定名為「{{lang|en|Fire Emblem Fates}}」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2015/06/16/e3-2015-fire-emblem-fates-coming-2016 |title = E3 2015: Fire Emblem: Fates Coming 2016 |last = Pitcher |first = Jenna |date = 2015-06-17 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161118/https://www.ign.com/articles/2015/06/16/e3-2015-fire-emblem-fates-coming-2016 |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref>。6月25日，任天堂在日本正式發售遊戲的《白夜王國》和《暗夜王國》<ref name="電撃@150402">{{Cite web |url = https://dengekionline.com/elem/000/001/032/1032585/ |script-title = ja:『ファイアーエムブレム if 白夜王国/暗夜王国』の発売日は6月25日！ |author = 電撃オンライン |date = 2015-04-02 |publisher = KADOKAWA Game Linkage |language = ja |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200805223141/https://dengekionline.com/elem/000/001/032/1032585/ |archivedate = 2020-08-05}}</ref>。購買任一實體版本的玩家可透過DLC的方式，用較低廉的價格增購另一版本<ref name="電撃@150402"/>。《透魔王國》在遊戲開賣後兩星期以DLC的形式於[[任天堂eShop|任天堂eShop]]作獨家發布<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.famitsu.com/news/201507/09082777.html |script-title = ja:『ファイアーエムブレムif』 第3のシナリオ“インビジブルキングダム”が配信開始 |date = 2015-07-09 |publisher = ファミ通.com |language = ja |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220131084642/https://www.famitsu.com/news/201507/09082777.html |archivedate = 2022-01-31}}</ref>。除了兩個標準版本外，任天堂亦推出了限量的特別版套裝，內含預載了三個版本的遊戲卡、畫集以及其他贈品<ref name="SEsoldout">{{Cite web |url = https://www.excite.co.jp/news/article/Inside_86521/ |script-title = ja:『ファイアーエムブレムif SPECIAL EDITION』追加出荷が決定…1日経たずに売り切れが続出した限定版 |date = 2015-04-04 |publisher = Excite |language = ja |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210304225631/https://www.excite.co.jp/news/article/Inside_86521/ |archivedate = 2021-03-04}}</ref>。11月6日，任天堂宣布即日在香港和臺灣推出《白夜王國》實體版，《暗夜王國》和DLC《透魔王國》則可經eShop下載<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=123411 |title = 香港任天堂宣布《聖火降魔錄 if》於繁體中文版 3DS 主機推出 |date = 2015-11-06 |publisher = 巴哈姆特電玩資訊站 |language = zh-tw |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220220103254/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=123411 |archivedate = 2022-02-20}}</ref>。任天堂在西方世界發行遊戲時亦參照日本的發布模式。2016年2月，任天堂在北美地區發行兩個實體版本遊戲，並在一個月後以DLC形式推出《透魔王國》<ref name="PolyInterview"/><ref name="Sato@Siliconera_160121">{{Cite web |url = http://www.siliconera.com/2016/01/21/nintendo-responds-changes-fire-emblem-fates-western-localization/ |title = Nintendo Responds To Changes To Fire Emblem Fates’ Western Localization |author = Sato |date = 2016-01-21 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160122085902/http://www.siliconera.com/2016/01/21/nintendo-responds-changes-fire-emblem-fates-western-localization/ |archivedate = 2016-01-22}}</ref>。同年5月20日，遊戲在歐洲開賣，而《透魔王國》則於6月9日發布<ref name=Casey@Siliconera_160303">{{Cite web |url = http://www.siliconera.com/2016/03/03/fire-emblem-fates-headed-europe-may-20/ |title = Fire Emblem Fates Is Headed To Europe On May 20 |author = Casey |date = 2016-03-03 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181001011117/http://www.siliconera.com/2016/03/03/fire-emblem-fates-headed-europe-may-20/ |archivedate = 2018-10-01}}</ref>。任天堂在北美和歐洲地區亦有推出特別版套裝<ref name=Casey@Siliconera_160303"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.gematsu.com/2015/11/fire-emblem-fates-launches-february-19-north-america |title = Fire Emblem Fates launches February 19 in North America |last = Romano |first = Sal |date = 2015-11-12 |publisher = Gematsu |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127135504/https://www.gematsu.com/2015/11/fire-emblem-fates-launches-february-19-north-america |archivedate = 2020-11-27}}</ref>。2022年2月16日，任天堂宣布逐步終止任天堂3DS的eShop數位內容購買服務，而遊戲所有DLC（包括追加下載地圖和《透魔王國》）的購買和下載亦將會在2023年3月下旬結束<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.siliconera.com/fire-emblem-fates-dlc-will-leave-nintendo-3ds-eshop-in-2023/ |title = Fire Emblem Fates DLC Will Leave Nintendo 3DS eShop in 2023 |last = Liu |first = Stephanie |date = 2022-02-16 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-21 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220216144528/https://www.siliconera.com/fire-emblem-fates-dlc-will-leave-nintendo-3ds-eshop-in-2023/ |archivedate = 2022-02-16}}</ref>。

在日本，任天堂推出以火焰之紋章系列為題的[[交換卡片遊戲|交換卡片遊戲]]和以《覺醒》為背景的漫畫來推廣遊戲<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.siliconera.com/2015/01/15/fire-emblem-also-gets-new-card-game-manga-japan/ |title = Fire Emblem Also Gets A New Card Game And Manga In Japan |author = Sato |date = 2015-01-15 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150706040350/http://www.siliconera.com/2015/01/15/fire-emblem-also-gets-new-card-game-manga-japan/ |archivedate = 2015-07-06}}</ref>。卡片遊戲的兩個入門包附有代碼，玩家輸入後便可以DLC形式來使用馬爾斯和露琪娜這兩個角色<ref name="Sato@Siliconera_150414">{{Cite web |url = http://www.siliconera.com/2015/04/14/marth-lucina-fire-emblem-dlc-characters/ |title = Marth And Lucina Are Fire Emblem If DLC Characters |author = Sato |date = 2015-04-14 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150626181353/http://www.siliconera.com/2015/04/14/marth-lucina-fire-emblem-dlc-characters/ |archivedate = 2015-06-26}}</ref>。同時該遊戲的擴張包亦附有首作角色米奈娃的代碼<ref name="Sato@Siliconera_150414"/>。另外，任天堂還推出了《if》的特別版[[新任天堂3DS|新任天堂3DS]]，以及獨立的可替換面板<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/newsclip/700185.html |script-title = ja:「ファイアーエムブレムif」のきせかえプレート、New 3DSのパックが発売決定 |date = 2015-04-30 |publisher = GAME Watch |language = ja |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210514041222/https://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/newsclip/700185.html |archivedate = 2021-05-14}}</ref>。遊戲於日本發售後，任天堂宣布同年9月會在《月刊Young Magazine》上連載以遊戲作背景的漫畫，並交由樹林執筆、小崎作畫<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.famitsu.com/news/201507/25084341.html |script-title = ja:『ファイアーエムブレム』コザキユースケ氏と樹林伸氏が手掛けるコミカライズ作品が、月刊ヤングマガジンで2015年9月より連載決定 |date = 2015-07-25 |publisher = ファミ通.com |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190831033055/https://www.famitsu.com/news/201507/25084341.html |archivedate = 2019-08-31}}</ref>。任天堂亦在2015年7月至9月期間發布了多張DLC地圖，部分與遊戲故事相關，也有一些是關於其他出現在舊作的角色<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.siliconera.com/2015/07/22/fire-emblem-fates-dlc-map-will-feature-characters-from-awakening/ |title = Fire Emblem Fates’ DLC Map Will Feature Characters From Awakening |author = Sato |date = 2015-07-22 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222202931/http://www.siliconera.com/2015/07/22/fire-emblem-fates-dlc-map-will-feature-characters-from-awakening/ |archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.siliconera.com/2015/01/15/fire-emblem-also-gets-new-card-game-manga-japan/ |title = Fire Emblem Also Gets A New Card Game And Manga In Japan |author = Sato |date = 2015-01-15 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151016041428/http://www.siliconera.com/2015/09/23/fire-emblem-fates-latest-dlc-maps-feature-series-merchant-girl-anna/ |archivedate = 2015-07-06}}</ref>。這些DLC地圖在北美和歐洲的推出時間分別是2016年2月至4月及同年5月中旬至7月下旬<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.siliconera.com/2016/01/27/fire-emblem-fates-dlc-schedule-released/ |title = Fire Emblem Fates DLC Schedule Released |last = Lada |first = Jenni |date = 2016-01-27 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160127193402/http://www.siliconera.com/2016/01/27/fire-emblem-fates-dlc-schedule-released/ |archivedate = 2016-01-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.siliconera.com/2016/05/16/fire-emblem-fates-awakening-dlc-arrive-europe-week/ |title = Fire Emblem Fates And The Before Awakening DLC Arrive In Europe This Week |last = Lada |first = Jenni |date = 2016-05-16 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160517095557/http://www.siliconera.com/2016/05/16/fire-emblem-fates-awakening-dlc-arrive-europe-week/ |archivedate = 2016-05-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.siliconera.com/2016/06/23/europe-gets-fire-emblem-fates-map-pack-2-july-21-2016/ |title = Europe Gets Fire Emblem Fates’ Map Pack 2 On July 21, 2016 |last = Lada |first = Jenni |date = 2016-06-23 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-14 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160624110643/http://www.siliconera.com/2016/06/23/europe-gets-fire-emblem-fates-map-pack-2-july-21-2016/ |archivedate = 2016-06-24}}</ref>。

遊戲的英語翻譯由任天堂（美國）的本地化分支公司任天堂樹屋負責<ref name="NinLocalFan">{{Cite web |url = https://www.destructoid.com/fire-emblem-fates-fan-translation-cancelled/ |title = Fire Emblem Fates fan-translation cancelled |last = Rowen |first = Nic |date = 2016-03-22 |publisher = Destructoid |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161219/https://www.destructoid.com/fire-emblem-fates-fan-translation-cancelled/ |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref>。任天堂樹屋在負責本地化的同時亦修改了部分遊戲內容。在日文版遊戲內，男性個人單位與女角索雷爾的支援對話被認為帶有[[LGBT迴轉治療|性傾向治療]]元素而備受批評<ref name="Sato@Siliconera_160121"/><ref name="NWR_NinMessage">{{Cite web |url = http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/41814/fire-emblem-fates-changes-controversial-support-conversation-in-western-regions |title = Fire Emblem: Fates Changes Controversial Support Conversation in Western Regions |last = Bonds |first = Curtis |date = 2016-01-20 |publisher = Nintendo World Report |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161122/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/41814/fire-emblem-fates-changes-controversial-support-conversation-in-western-regions |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref>。為了避免引起爭議，任天堂樹屋在英語版遊戲內刪除了這類帶有類似元素的支援對話<ref name="Sato@Siliconera_160121"/><ref name="NWR_NinMessage"/>。英語版本亦刪走了玩家在個人房間透過觸控螢幕「撫摸」特定角色的臉頰來增加好感度的小遊戲元素，但2D互動和好感度提升則獲保留<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.siliconera.com/2016/01/26/western-versions-fire-emblem-fates-lacks-touching-minigame/ |title = Western Version of Fire Emblem Fates Lacks Touching Minigame |last = Lada |first = Jenni |date = 2016-01-26 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-15 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160126205356/http://www.siliconera.com/2016/01/26/western-versions-fire-emblem-fates-lacks-touching-minigame/ |archivedate = 2016-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.polygon.com/2016/2/4/10920292/fire-emblem-fates-petting-skinship-localization-change |title = Here's how Nintendo changed 'petting' in Fire Emblem Fates |last1 = Frank |first1 = Allegra |last2 = Robinson |first2 = Nick |date = 2016-02-04 |publisher = Polygon |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161217/https://www.polygon.com/2016/2/4/10920292/fire-emblem-fates-petting-skinship-localization-change |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref>。同遭刪除的還有曾在《覺醒》出現的日語配音選項<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.polygon.com/2016/2/5/10925232/fire-emblem-fates-japanese-language-dual-audio-western-release |title = Fire Emblem Fates won't have Japanese voice option in Western release |last1 = Frank |first1 = Allegra |last2 = Robinson |first2 = Nick |date = 2016-02-05 |publisher = Polygon |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220109034151/https://www.polygon.com/2016/2/5/10925232/fire-emblem-fates-japanese-language-dual-audio-western-release |archivedate = 2022-01-09}}</ref>。任天堂（美國）發出聲明，指必要時還會更改其他未有指明的內容<ref name="Sato@Siliconera_160121"/>。英語版遊戲發行後，粉絲把它與原版比對，最終發現並指出一連串內容變化<ref name="NinLocalFan"/><ref name="IGNfates">{{Cite web |url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2016/03/31/nintendo-terminates-fire-emblem-fates-spokesperson |title = Nintendo Terminates Fire Emblem Fates Spokesperson |last = Otero first = Jose |date = 2016-03-31 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512235422/https://www.ign.com/articles/2016/03/31/nintendo-terminates-fire-emblem-fates-spokesperson |archivedate = 2021-05-12}}</ref>。此事在互聯網上引起軒然大波，不少玩家因而直接向任天堂作出投訴<ref name="NinLocalFan"/><ref name="IGNfates"/>。這也促使粉絲組成「{{lang|en|Team if}}」團隊著手進行更忠於原著的非官方翻譯，但不久後他們便停止所有翻譯工作<ref name="NinLocalFan"/>。

