/best-of-2016-awards/Best_Strategy_Game |title = Best Strategy Game |date = 2017-01-07 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161225/https://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2016-awards/Best_Strategy_Game |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref>。在GameSpot的2016年度遊戲獎上，遊戲入選最佳3DS遊戲五強<ref name="GSaward2016_Best3DSgame">{{Cite web |url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-best-3ds-games-of-2016/1100-6446140/ |title = The Best 3DS Games of 2016 |last = Espineli |first = Matt |date = 2016-12-12 |publisher = GameSpot |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161127/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-best-3ds-games-of-2016/1100-6446140/ |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref>。而在[[遊戲開發者選擇獎|遊戲開發者選擇獎]]上，遊戲入圍最佳移動／掌上遊戲<ref name="GDCA2016">{{Cite web |url = https://www.gamechoiceawards.com/archive/gdca_17th |title = 17th Annual Game Developers Choice Awards |publisher = Game Developers Conference |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220210085119/https://www.gamechoiceawards.com/archive/gdca_17th|archivedate = 2022-02-10}}</ref>。

== 影響 ==
2016年2月，遊戲主角神威在跨界格鬥遊戲《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥3DS/Wii_U|任天堂明星大亂鬥3DS/Wii U]]》中以追加下載角色的身份登場<ref name="FEFsmash">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2015/12/corrin_chooses_to_fight_in_super_smash_bros_for_wii_u_and_3ds |title = Corrin Chooses to Fight in Super Smash Bros. for Wii U and 3DS |last = Karklins |first = Andrew |date = 2015-12-16 |publisher = Nintendo Life |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200222162926/https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2015/12/corrin_chooses_to_fight_in_super_smash_bros_for_wii_u_and_3ds |archivedate = 2020-02-22}}</ref>。玩家在該作可選擇男性或女性版本的神威出戰<ref name="FEFsmash"/>。在該作的3DS版本中，這次的追加下載內容還包括兩首額外的本作配樂以及兩個獎杯<ref name="FEFsmash"/>。另外，神威在其續作《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥_特別版|任天堂明星大亂鬥 特別版]]》內同樣以可玩角色登場<ref name="FEFsmashu">{{Cite web |url = https://kotaku.com/super-smash-bros-ultimate-will-star-every-character-fr-1826762767 |title = Super Smash Bros. Ultimate Will Star Every Character From Every Smash |last = D'Anastasio |first = Cecilia |date = 2018-06-12 |publisher = Kotaku |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220109113129/https://kotaku.com/super-smash-bros-ultimate-will-star-every-character-fr-1826762767 |archivedate = 2022-01-09}}</ref>。本作不少角色也陸續在跨界手機遊戲《[[火焰之紋章_英雄|火焰之紋章 英雄]]》和啟發自[[無雙系列遊戲列表|無雙系列]]的砍殺遊戲《[[聖火降魔錄無雙|聖火降魔錄無雙]]》亮相<ref name="FEFheroes">{{Cite web |url = https://www.vg247.com/fire-emblem-heroes-introduces-new-heroes |title = Fire Emblem Heroes introduces a few new heroes |last = Lemon |first = Marshall |date = 2018-04-23 |publisher = VG247 |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161135/https://www.vg247.com/fire-emblem-heroes-introduces-new-heroes |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref><ref name="FEFwarriors">{{Cite web |url = https://www.siliconera.com/fire-emblem-warriors-adds-fire-emblem-fates-characters/ |title = Fire Emblem Warriors Adds Fire Emblem Fates Characters |last = Lada |first = Jenni |date = 2017-06-13 |publisher = Siliconera |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220220074217/https://www.siliconera.com/fire-emblem-warriors-adds-fire-emblem-fates-characters/ |archivedate = 2022-02-20}}</ref>。2017年7月，任天堂推出了以任天堂明星大亂鬥系列為主題的神威雙性別版本Amiibo<ref name="CorrinAmiibo">{{Cite web |url = https://www.famitsu.com/news/201704/13130972.html |script-title = ja:『ゼルダの伝説』から3種類のリンクのamiiboが6月22日に、『スマブラ』からクラウド、カムイ、ベヨネッタのamiiboが7月22日に発売決定！【Nintendo Direct】 |date = 2017-04-13 |publisher = ファミ通.com |language = ja |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200622130526/https://www.famitsu.com/news/201704/13130972.html |archivedate = 2020-06-22}}</ref>。在2017年4月發行的《[[火焰之纹章_回声_另一位英雄王|火焰之纹章 回声 另一位英雄王]]》內，玩家可掃瞄神威Amiibo，並在戰鬥中召喚其幻影作為臨時盟友<ref name="FEESoV_Amiibo1">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nintendo.com/en_CA/amiibo/games/detail/fire-emblem-echoes-shadows-of-valentia-3ds/ |title = Fire Emblem Echoes: Shadows of Valentia amiibo features |publisher = Nintendo |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210613085333/https://www.nintendo.com/en_CA/amiibo/games/detail/fire-emblem-echoes-shadows-of-valentia-3ds/ |archivedate = 2021-06-13}}</ref><ref name="FEESoV_Amiibo2">{{Cite web |url = https://www.monamiibo.com/how-to-use-amiibo-in-fire-emblem-echoes/ |title = Fire Emblem Echoes: Shadows of Valentia amiibo Usage Guide |last = Whittington |first = Joshua |date = 2017-06-20 |publisher = Mon Amiibo |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220220080335/https://www.monamiibo.com/how-to-use-amiibo-in-fire-emblem-echoes/ |archivedate = 2022-02-20}}</ref>。玩家亦可以在2019年7月發行的《[[火焰之纹章_风花雪月|火焰之纹章 风花雪月]]》內掃瞄Amiibo，並在支線任務中解鎖本作的配樂<ref name="FETH_Amiibo">{{Cite web |url = https://www.vg247.com/fire-emblem-three-houses-amiibo-unlocks-gazebo |title = Fire Emblem Three Houses amiibo unlocks: what every amiibo does at the gazebo |last = Donaldson |first = Alex |date = 2019-08-09 |publisher = VG247 |language = en |accessdate = 2022-02-20 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110161116/https://www.vg247.com/fire-emblem-three-houses-amiibo-unlocks-gazebo |archivedate = 2022-01-10}}</ref>。

